    <!--
        Curated list of Russian banking, government, telco, transport,
        delivery, media and marketplace apps known or suspected to
        fingerprint VPN/proxy state via ConnectivityManager.TRANSPORT_VPN,
        VpnTransportInfo, dumpsys vpn_management, GeoIP/ASN, etc.

        Adding these to PerAppMode.BLACKLIST means the listed apps see the
        real underlying network instead of the tunnel - their IP/GeoIP
        stays consistent with the SIM/Wi-Fi region and they do not see a
        VPN flag on the active network. This is the only client-side
        mitigation available without root: the OS-level VPN flag itself
        cannot be hidden by an app from another app.

        Wrong package names are silently skipped at runtime - the UI
        button calls getPackageInfo() per entry, so the toast count
        reflects only apps actually installed on this device.
    -->
